DEDICATED REAR-WHEEL DRIVE PLATFORMS


A perfect combination of striking vehicle proportions and exceptionally engaging driving experience is created on dedicated rear-wheel-drive platforms.

















ADVANCED ALL-WHEEL DRIVE


By virtue of its available all-wheel-drive system HTRAC, Genesis is agile and secure on any road surface.

















