functionality, providing a differentiated design through
displaying athletic elegance in design without compromise.




















Akin to the moment when an archer focuses his entire strength and spirit into the tip of an arrow, Genesis vehicles are designed to embody the breathtaking beauty of energy exploding with masterful control.

















